A photorealistic quadruped military robot with mechanical legs traversing a snowy mountainous terrain, its metallic joints and hydraulic systems gleaming against the white landscape, steam rising from its machinery in the cold air, dramatic winter storm clouds gathering in the background, the robot's silhouette reminiscent of a mechanical pack mule carrying military equipment, deep footprints left in the pristine snow behind it, golden hour lighting breaking through the clouds casting long shadows across the frozen wilderness.
